title: LEAGUE NOT WORKING
body: Okay so recently I just got back into playing League but for someone reason whenever I try and open it up on my computer it's always stuck on the LoLPatcherUx at the party where you're suppose to press "Launch". But for some unknown reasons it's not coming up, along with "online" and "oceania".... Can someone please help me? I have a MacBook Pro.

replies.body:
Hey caitiejayne,

This may be an issue caused by your client not being able to connect to the League of Legends servers. Can you try the solutions in the [**Troubleshooting Connection Issues**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues#section-mac) Riot Games Support article and let me know if anything works?
hey could u help out pls, I'm currently on a mac book pro,,and when i click on league, it pops  up but then it disappears after few seconds... and then nothing happens, Please and thank you!
